	<h1 class="title">《神探夏洛克》圣诞电影要在内地上映了，可能会成为票房黑马</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-25 16:21:25 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19730/medium/19730.jpeg?1451025669" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


